未必可釋放<br />\n都使你心中有罪 難以制止 忘掉方向 殺戮戰場」<br />\n<br />\n作曲作詞一手包辦，15年前的作品竟似是反映了現時香港的社會狀況。<br />\n<br />\n早前黃貫中宣布退出明年成軍37年演唱會，被指有不少樂迷不滿沒有黃家強在陣內，有消費Beyond隊名之嫌。但對此，黃家強並沒有多加理會。"},{"pid":"ac1f62f640cf759fb9498c5354887b777f4c483b","tid":1797766,"uid":76159,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"19d3ed7fc5e52af230a87d0b7dbaaf48b46ff7e7","tid":1797766,"uid":263798,"like":59,"dislike":0,"score":59,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T00:32:50.000Z","msg":"7,8年前Paul仲係反政府<br />\n當時仲有去遊行，同Hardpack拍mv屌鳩政府<br />\n依家影都無撚埋"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T02:03:13.000Z","msg":"因為哩幾年同朱茵生咗個女<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68a21b35f7eb925bc6c68ea0c65bf256aa3caaf3","tid":1797766,"uid":76159,"like":1,"dislike":13,"score":-12,"quote":{"pid":"45d5c503e2cfda805d0b96e3187c15bea025d757","tid":1797766,"uid":80650,"like":17,"dislike":7,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T01:54:33.000Z","msg":"估唔到家強先係同路人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n奶共Paul收皮啦屌你老母<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images-news.now.com/newsimage/NewsImage/2019-11-13-13-41-37R1yCbW4R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-news.now.com%2Fnewsimage%2FNewsImage%2F2019-11-13-13-41-37R1yCbW4R.jpg&h=8ad09c81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/entertainment/player?newsId=369729\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Fentertainment%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D369729&d=TvOq0m68uPCtaVYdNLQuFAuBxQMtbc6xR8MkqxZcasw%3D&h=305b72ad\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Fentertainment%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D369729&h=32b4f64c\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/entertainment/player?newsId=369729</a><br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://Now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FNow.com&d=TvOq0m68uPCtaVYdNLQuFAuBxQMtbc6xR8MkqxZcasw%3D&h=437f1a15\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Now.com</a>娛樂】Beyon